io.github.struppigel.parser.coffheader

Enum MachineType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MachineType>
      • io.github.struppigel.parser.coffheader.MachineType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Characteristic, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MachineType>

    public enum MachineType
extends java.lang.Enum<MachineType>
implements Characteristic
    Represents the machine the image file can run on.

    Descriptions are from the PECOFF specification.
